data.name: intro1.Text
data.value: Vifarnet Fix It is an app. specially built to manage and help the users, know and fix any computer related problems, at any circumstances, without misleading or harming your Personal Computer. It is user friendly, and more convenient to use. What's more, it uses NONE of your system resources or files, to avoid further blunders and also to make sure that system damages don't affect Vifarnet.

data.name: intro2.Text
data.value: Type your problems below, and Vifarnet Search will give a precise solution to the problem. Remember that Vifarnet Search is highly accurate and sensitive. DO NOT commit any grammatical errors. If you want to give a brief description or if you are aware of your problem, choose Advanced Search.
